            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 25 chamber: Enriched uranium oxide, for which the",
                "ratio of 235U to 238U was about 1 to 8, was sprayed",
                "onto each side of the foils to the thickness of 1 mg",
                "per cm2 of uranium. There was a total of 7.74 gm of",
                "uranium in a chamber, of which about 0.89 gram was",
                "235U."
              ]
            }
          ],
