              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "92-U-235",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.1374
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A sample of uranium oxides",
                "enriched in 25, was used. The amount of 235U",
                "contained in the sample was 13.74% by weight of the",
                "total amount of uranium present. The entire sample of",
                "the oxide weighed 309.6 gm., but was divided into two",
                "parts. These two parts, designated as #l and #2",
                "contained approximately two third and one thirds,",
                "respectively, of the total amount. The samples were",
                "placed in cylindrical aluminum containers having an",
                "inside diameter of 2.50 inches. Two other samples,#3",
                "and #4 were made of normal tuballoy oxide. These were",
                "placed in containers similar the enriched samples."
              ]
            }
          ],
